name: UCO Titan Stormproof Matches
description: These matches burn tenaciously and will relight even after several seconds of complete submersion. A great addition to any emergency kit.Includes 25 matches and 2 extra strikers.Easy to light and will relight after being submerged.If matches are wet, just wipe dry before lighting (striker needs to be dry to light).Up to 25 second burn time.Extended length (10.5cm) prevents burning your fingertips.Note: match will not extinguish until chemical has burned out, should be doused in water to completely extinguish.
